user_text: Amazing little deli in Jersey City. If you are looking for an authentic place this is it. Every time i am hungry and want something fast i always end up going there to grab a chimi (Dominican sandwhich) which is also, very filling.
They just delivered two sandwiches $10bucks! Amazing in less 15 mins! So delicious please try this place!

Went 2 days ago for the 1st time. Â I ordered both a chimi sandwich and a chicken chimi sandwich, it was great!! The bread toasty but soft, the sauce was just delicious! Only 3 stars because I have to try the other items on their menu.
A real Dominican Chimi in New Jersey done the right way !
